in the hall to the right of the throne chair, they had to pull him into the main room where we took him before.  From what I figure is he didnt gate for us; either time, because we killed him basically where he spawned.  <br><br>To keep him from gating again, they had the pallys try stun him.  In order to do this, they would have had to be within AOE range.  <br><br>Something else interesting happened... when he got to about 1/4 health they told the casters to start nuking him.  They did and some of those who did died.  They did call off the casters and had the pets finished him off.  It seems as if pets killing him is the best way to handle this guy.<br><br>Symira<br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub88.ezboard.com/fepicheroes73161frm16.showPrevMessage?topicID=40.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub88.ezboard.com/fepicheroes73161frm16.showNextMessage?topicID=40.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub88.ezboard.com/fepicheroes73161frm16.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=40.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub88.ezboard.com/fepicheroes73161frm16.emailToFriend?topicID=40.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub88.ezboard.com/fepicheroes73161frm16.threadControl?topicID=40.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub88.ezboard.com/fepicheroes73161frm16.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=40.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub88.ezboard.com/fepicheroes73161frm16.unsubscribe